Source: apport
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: cdbs (>= 0.4.43), debhelper (>= 5.0.37.2), python-support (>= 0.3), python-dev (>= 2.4), intltool
Maintainer: Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@ubuntu.com>
Standards-Version: 3.7.2
